reviews.review_text: Dark Star This is quite possibly the best DS I have heard...
Dark Star - mind melt Always loved this show.  Bury me with this one.  Sacred stuff!

Veneta '72 Incredible show.  Although everybody and their great aunt has this show, however it really should have been an official release along the way...This is a nice sounding source...soundboard...as for the music, it can be argued that the china>rider, playin', bird song, sing me back home and dark star are the best versions ever played of each respective tune...the band jams with drive and intuition, many psychadelic moments...rest of the show ain't too shabby either...

Sunshine Daydream 1st set
Good Promised Land opener.
Very hot China > Rider
I like BERTHA as a 1st set closer.
This is DEAD SHOW meets RAINBOW GATHERING!

No Rainbow Gathering This is real hippies, not a bunch of scammers and trolls in the mountains.  

This is a historic concert, great all the way through  Not much else can be said about it.  The whole stretch from BCT through September is very hot.
- One of the greatest shows this band ever played, reputation more than deserved! Every song is a gem, the energy crackles and turns the world.
